### Remediation & Hardening
Enforce SMB Signing: Stops the relay attacks used to pivot across servers.

Rotate KRBTGT: A double-reset of the krbtgt password is now required to invalidate forged tickets.

Tiered Administration: Ensure high-privileged accounts never log in to lower-tier workstations.
